The \(\text{p}\overline{\text{p}}\) collision cross-section \(\sigma_{\text{p}\overline{\text{p}}} \approx 30 \, \text{mb} = 3 \times 10^{-26} \, \text{cm}^2\), thus the number of \(\text{p}\overline{\text{p}}\) annihilation events per second is
\[
