problem:
In the SLAC (Stanford Linear Collider) at the Stanford National Accelerator Laboratory in the USA, the center-of-mass energy can reach 90 GeV, which is the mass of the \(Z^{0}\) boson, to produce the neutral vector boson \(Z^{0}\). The \(Z^{0}\) decays into a pair of leptons or quarks, and the coupling Lagrangian density with related particles is given by

\[
\begin{aligned}
L_{Z}= & \frac{\mathrm{i} g}{4 \cos \theta_{\mathrm{W}}} Z^{\mu}\left\{\bar{\nu} \gamma_{\mu}\left(1-\gamma_{5}\right) \nu+\overline{\mathrm{e}} \gamma_{\mu}\left[\left(4 \sin ^{2} \theta_{\mathrm{W}}-1\right)-\gamma_{5}\right] e\right. \\
& \left.+\bar{\mu} \gamma_{\mu}\left[\left(1-\frac{8}{3} \sin ^{2} \theta_{\mathrm{W}}\right)+\gamma_{5}\right] \mu+\bar{d} \gamma_{\mu}\left[\left(\frac{4}{3} \sin ^{2} \theta_{\mathrm{W}}-1\right)-\gamma_{5}\right] d\right\}
\end{aligned}
\]

Here, \((\nu, e)\) and \((u, d)\) denote the creation operators for leptons and quarks, respectively. The relationship of the coupling constant is given by \(G_{\mathrm{F}}=\frac{g^{2} \sqrt{2}}{8 M_{\mathrm{W}}^{2}}\), where \(M_{\mathrm{W}}=80 \, \mathrm{GeV}\).

Provide the total cross section as a function of the total center-of-mass energy \(s=E^{2}\) for the neutrino production process.

solution:
设两 $\gamma$ 光子的动量和能量分别为 $p_{\gamma_1}, p_{\gamma_2}$ 和 $E_{\gamma_1}, E_{\gamma_2}$，$\pi^0$ 粒子的动量和能量分别为 $p_\pi$ 和 $E$，根据能量和动量守恒，要求

$$
\begin{aligned}
E &= E_{\gamma_1} + E_{\gamma_2}, \\
p_\pi &= p_{\gamma_1} - p_{\gamma_2}, \\
E^2 &= p_\pi^2 + m_\pi^2, \quad E_{\gamma_1} = p_{\gamma_1}, \quad E_{\gamma_2} = p_{\gamma_2}, \\
m_{\pi}^2 &= 4E_{\gamma_1}E_{\gamma_2} = 4E_{\gamma_1}(E - E_{\gamma_1})
\end{aligned}
$$

由上面的方程可得解，得两 $\gamma$ 光子的能量为

$$
\begin{aligned}
E_{\gamma_1} &= \frac{E+\sqrt{E^2-m_\pi^2}}{2} = \frac{1000+\sqrt{1000^2-135^2}}{2} \approx 995.4 \ \mathrm{MeV}, \\
E_{\gamma_2} &= \frac{E-\sqrt{E^2-m_\pi^2}}{2} = \frac{1000-\sqrt{1000^2-135^2}}{2} \approx 4.6 \ \mathrm{MeV}
\end{aligned}
$$

根据类氢原子能级公式：

$$
\begin{gathered}
E_{n} = -\frac{Z^{2}}{n^{2}} \times 13.6 \, \text{eV} \\
Z = 2, \, n = 1 \\
E_{\mathrm{I}} = 4 \times 13.6 = 54.4 \, \text{eV}
\end{gathered}
$$

得到 He 的第二电离能为 54.4 eV。

跃迁中的最长和最短波长分别为

\[
\begin{gathered}
\tilde{\nu}_{\max }=\frac{1}{\lambda_{1}}=\frac{E_{4}-E_{1}}{h c}=R\left(\frac{5}{9}+\frac{119}{108} \alpha^{2}\right), \quad \lambda_{1}=\left(\frac{5}{9} R+\frac{119}{108} R \alpha^{2}\right)^{-1} \\
\tilde{\nu}_{\min }=\frac{1}{\lambda_{2}}=\frac{E_{3}-E_{2}}{h c}=R\left(\frac{5}{9}-\frac{7}{36} \alpha^{2}\right), \quad \lambda_{2}=\left(\frac{5}{9} R-\frac{7}{36} R \alpha^{2}\right)^{-1}
\end{gathered}
\]

波长差为

\[
\Delta \lambda=\lambda_{2}-\lambda_{1}=0.0204 \, \mathrm{nm}
\]

也可以由光谱项直接求出：

\[
\begin{gathered}
\Delta T_{n l}=\frac{R \alpha^{2} Z^{4}}{n^{3} l(l+1)} \\
\therefore \Delta T_{2 \mathrm{p}}=\frac{R \alpha^{2} \times 2^{4}}{2^{3} \times 1 \times 2}=R \alpha^{2} \\
\Delta T_{3 \mathrm{p}}=\frac{R \alpha^{2} \times 2^{4}}{3^{3} \times 1 \times 2}=\frac{8}{27} R \alpha^{2}
\end{gathered}
\]

不考虑精细结构： \(\tilde{\nu}=\frac{1}{\lambda}=\left(\frac{1}{2^{2}}-\frac{1}{3^{2}}\right) R Z^{2}=\frac{5}{9} R\)

\[
\Delta \lambda=\lambda_{2}-\lambda_{1}=\frac{\tilde{\nu}_{1}-\tilde{\nu}_{2}}{\tilde{\nu}^{2}}=\frac{\Delta T_{2 \mathrm{p}}+\Delta T_{3 \mathrm{p}}}{\tilde{\nu}^{2}}=\frac{21 \alpha^{2}}{5 R} \approx 0.0204 \, \mathrm{nm}
\]

锂原子的谱项为

$$
T_{2 \mathrm{s}}=\frac{R}{\left(2-\Delta_{\mathrm{s}}\right)^{2}}, \quad T_{2 \mathrm{p}}=\frac{R}{\left(2-\Delta_{\mathrm{p}}\right)^{2}}
$$

2 p态到 2 s态跃迁的谱线波数为

$$
\begin{aligned}
\tilde{\nu}_{2 \mathrm{p} \rightarrow 2 \mathrm{s}} & = T_{2 \mathrm{s}} - T_{2 \mathrm{p}} = \frac{R}{\left(2-\Delta_{\mathrm{s}}\right)^{2}} - \frac{R}{\left(2-\Delta_{\mathrm{p}}\right)^{2}} \\
& = \frac{13.6 \times 10^{10}}{12400 \times (2-0.40)^{2}} - \frac{13.6 \times 10^{10}}{12400 \times (2-0.05)^{2}} \\
& = 1.40 \times 10^{6} \, \mathrm{m}^{-1}
\end{aligned}
$$

The energy required to dissociate a KCl molecule into K and Cl atoms is obtained by subtracting the energy needed to convert $\mathrm{K}^{+}$ into a K atom (which is the first ionization energy of potassium) from the energy required to dissociate it into $\mathrm{K}^{+}$ and $\mathrm{Cl}^{-}$ ions, and then adding the energy needed for $\mathrm{Cl}^{-}$ to lose an electron, which is the electron affinity of chlorine. This yields:

$$
\begin{aligned}
E_{\mathrm{KCl}} = E_{\mathrm{dissociate}} - E_{\mathrm{K}^{+}} + E_{\mathrm{Cl}^{-}} = 5.16 \mathrm{\,eV} - 4.34 \mathrm{\,eV} + 3.82 \mathrm{\,eV} = 4.64 \mathrm{\,eV}
\end{aligned}
$$

在 $\eta^{\prime}$ 静止参考系中，守恒定律得出

$$
\begin{gathered}
E_{\mathrm{p}}^{*}=M-E^{*}, \quad p_{\mathrm{p}}^{*}=p^{*} \\
E_{\mathrm{p}}^{* 2}-p_{\mathrm{p}}^{* 2}=m^{2}=M^{2}-2 M E^{*} \\
E^{*}=\frac{M^{2}-m^{2}}{2 M}
\end{gathered}
$$

能量的洛伦兹变换为

$$
\begin{aligned}
E^{*} & =\gamma E(\theta)(1-\beta \cos \theta) \\
E(\theta) & =\frac{E^{*}}{\gamma(1-\beta \cos \theta)}=\frac{M^{2}-m^{2}}{2\left(E_{\eta}-p_{\eta} \cos \theta\right)}
\end{aligned}
$$
